item.title: Jackson x Imelda
item.description: This pairing was between our fourth generation hold back, Jackson, and our female from Ramblin’ Exotics, Imelda. Imelda is a great mix of WC Gambit lines and Kammerflage Kreations yellow-bodied blue bar Ambilobe while Jackson is the most vibrant male from our Jack x Mavokely clutch. We will definitely keep this line in our project in the years to come! Hatch dates 7/14/2022 - 8/16/2022 Hatch rate 29/38 F1
